A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Environment – Maryland Water Quality Revolving Loan Fund – Renaming and
3 Alterations
4 FOR the purpose of renaming the Maryland Water Quality Revolving Loan Fund to be the
5 Maryland Water Quality Improvement Revolving Loan Fund; altering the conditions
6 under which the Fund may be used to include supporting certain projects; requiring
7 the Maryland Water Infrastructure Financing Administration to include certain
8 communities and to use a certain scoring system when creating a certain intended
9 use plan; and generally relating to the Maryland Water Quality Improvement
10 Revolving Loan Fund.
